02.cms|title=When Leonardo Dicaprio, Cameron Diaz were plagued by OCD|first=Zeenia|last=Baria|date=17 January 2017|publisher=[[The Times of India]]}}</ref>\n\n== E ==\n*[[Jesse Eisenberg]], American actor<ref>{{cite web|first=Gwilym|last=Mumford|title=Jesse Eisenberg on Woody Allen, anxiety and fatherhood: 'Now I get to worry about something visible'|date=14 September 2018|work=[[The Guardian]]|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2018/sep/14/jesse-eisenberg-on-woody-allen-anxiety-and-fatherhood}}</ref>\n*[[Missy Elliott]], American rapper who suffered from anxiety disorder<ref name=independent/>\n*[[Chris Evans (actor)|Chris Evans]], American actor<ref>{{cite web|first=Jessica|last=Contrera|title=Kristen Bell and Chris Evans interviews highlight what happens when celebrities talk about depression|date=9 May 2016|work=The Independent|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/kristen-bell-chris-evans-and-what-happens-when-celebrities-talk-about-anxiety-and-depression-a7019891.html}}</ref>\n*[[George Ezra]], British singer-songwriter who struggles with anxiety<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nme.com/news/music/george-ezra-returns-comeback-single-paradise-2222055|title=George Ezra returns with comeback single 'Paradise'|last=Reilly|first=Nick|date=19 January 2018|website=[[NME]]|accessdate=10 May 2018}}</ref>\n\n== F ==\n*[[Harrison Ford]], American actor who suffered from [[social anxiety disorder]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.healthcentral.com/article/celebrities-with-anxiety-harrison-ford-fear-of-public-speaking|title=Celebrities with Anxiety: Harrison Ford: Fear of Public Speaking|last=Bailey|first=Eileen|date=7 August 2008|website=HealthCentral}}</ref>\n\n== G ==\n*[[Lady Gaga]], American musician and actress who has suffered from depression and anxiety<ref>{{cite web|author=Billboard |url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/magazine-feature/6730027/lady-gaga-billboard-cover-born-this-way-foundation-depression-philanthropy |title=Lady Gaga on Born This Wa