66|title=Howie Mandel 'Deals' Publicly With OCD|first=A. B. C.|last=News|date=1 December 2009|website=ABC News}}</ref>\n*[[John Mayer]], American singer and musician<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.everydayhealth.com/anxiety-pictures/celebrities-with-anxiety-disorders.aspx#08|title=Famous People Get Anxious, Too - Mental Health Awareness|website=Everyday Health}}</ref>\n*[[Shawn Mendes]], Canadian singer-songwriter who suffered with anxiety disorder<ref>https://www.teenvogue.com/story/shawn-mendes-coping-anxiety</ref>\n\n== O ==\n*[[Donny Osmond]], American singer and actor<ref>{{cite web |title=Donny Osmond Confronts Panic - 48 Hours |url=https://www.cbsnews.com/news/donny-osmond-confronts-panic/ |website=[[CBS News]] |accessdate=15 May 2019 |date=24 February 2000}}</ref>\n\n== P ==\n*[[Michelle Pfeiffer]], American actress who struggled with [[social anxiety disorder]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.etonline.com/michelle-pfeiffer-opens-about-her-social-anxiety-admits-she-first-found-fame-terrifying-89105|title=Michelle Pfeiffer Opens Up About Her Social Anxiety, Admits She First Found Fame 'Terrifying'|last=Willis|first=Jackie|date=12 October 2017|website=[[Entertainment Tonight]]}}</ref>\n\n== R ==\n*[[Lili Reinhart]], American actress<ref>{{cite web |last1=Framke |first1=Caroline |title=Why Lili Reinhart Isn\u2019t Afraid to Speak Out on Mental Health and Body Issues |url=https://variety.com/2018/tv/features/lili-reinhart-riverdale-mental-health-body-issues-1202916764/ |website=Variety |accessdate=10 May 2019 |language=en |date=28 August 2018}}</ref>\n*[[Jon Richardson]], English comedian who suffered from obsessive-compulsive disorder<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thevisitor.co.uk/news/jon-richardson-returns-to-morecambe-winter-gardens-for-lancaster-hospice-1-7966005|title=Jon Richardson returns to Morecambe Winter Gardens for Lancaster hospice|last=Sherlock|first=Gemma|date=15 June 2016|website=[[The Visitor (newspaper)|The Visitor]]}}</ref>\n*[[LeAnn Rimes]], 