0027/lady-gaga-billboard-cover-born-this-way-foundation-depression-philanthropy |title=Lady Gaga on Born This Way Foundation, Suffering From Depression |publisher=Billboard |date=2015-10-15 |accessdate=2018-04-20}}</ref>\n*[[Paul Gascoigne]], English footballer who suffered with anxiety<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mirror.co.uk/news/world-news/paul-gascoigne-detox-hell-hallucinations-1703970|title=\"Hallucinations, tremors, insomnia, anxiety and paranoia\": Gazza's detox hell|first=Jeremy|last=Armstrong|date=11 February 2013|publisher=}}</ref>\n*[[Whoopi Goldberg]], American actress and television personality<ref>{{cite web |last1=Orzessek |first1=Eli |title=Flying away from fear: Overcoming a phobia of air travel |url=https://www.nzherald.co.nz/travel/news/article.cfm?c_id=7&objectid=12051052 |date=15 May 2018 |website=[[The New Zealand Herald]] |accessdate=9 April 2019 |language=en-NZ}}</ref>\n*[[Selena Gomez]], American singer and actress<ref>{{cite web |title=Selena Gomez Gets Real About Anxiety\u2014And How Therapy Changed Everything |url=https://www.vogue.com/article/selena-gomez-rehab-therapy-mental-health-depression |website=[[Vogue (magazine)|Vogue]] |date=16 March 2017|accessdate=9 April 2019}}</ref>\n*[[Zack Greinke]], American baseball pitcher<ref>{{cite web |last1=Berg |first1=Ted |title=Zack Greinke: 'Every year, I get nervous that it's not working good enough' |url=https://ftw.usatoday.com/2018/03/zack-greinke-spring-training-arizona-diamondbacks-velocity-performance-mlb |website=For The Win |publisher=USA Today Sports |accessdate=17 May 2019 |language=en |date=8 March 2018}}</ref>\n\n== H ==\n*[[Colton Haynes]], American actor<ref>{{cite web |last1=Heller |first1=Corinne |title=Colton Haynes Talks About Battling Anxiety and Agoraphobia |url=https://www.eonline.com/news/720569/colton-haynes-opens-up-about-his-struggles-with-anxiety-and-agoraphobia |website=[[E! Online]] |accessdate=5 April 2019 |date=2 December 2015}}</ref>\n*[[Taraji P. Henson]], A